#set($layout = "_index.vm")
#set($page_title = "发表 Blog - By smile zino")
#set($active = "blog")

<style>
	#md-help {margin-top:90px}
	#md-help li{line-height:180%}
	.cmd-btn {margin:10px 0}
</style>
<link href='$link.js("markdown/wmd.css")' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'/>
<script src='$link.js("markdown/wmd.js")' type='text/javascript'></script>
<script src='$link.js("markdown/showdown.js")' type='text/javascript'></script>

<form>
<div class="row">
	<div class="span8">
		<input class="input-block-level" type="text" name="title" placeholder="标题"/>
		<div id="wmd-editor" class="wmd-panel">
			<div id="wmd-button-bar"></div>
			<textarea id="wmd-input" name="text"></textarea>
		</div>
		<h4>预览：</h4>
		<div id="wmd-preview" class="wmd-panel"></div>
    </div>
    
	<div class="span4" id="md-help">
		<div class="span3" style="float:right">
			<div class="well">
			<ul class="unstyled">
	           <li>行尾2空格 + 1回车 = 换行</li>
	           <li>连续2回车 = 空行分段</li>
	           <li>*斜体* ， **粗体**</li>
	           <li>行首4空格 = 代码块</li>
	           <li>行首&gt; = 引用</li>
	           <li>行首- = 无序列表</li>
	           <li>行首1. = 有序列表</li>
	           <li>&lt;http://foo.com&gt; = 链接网址</li>
	           <li>[文字](http://url) = 链接文字 </li>
	           <li>![说明](http://imgurl) = 图片</li>
	        </ul>
	        </div>
	     </div>
	     <div class="clearfix"></div>
	     <h4>HTML 代码：</h4>
	     <div id="wmd-output" class="wmd-panel"></div>      
    </div>
    <div class="cmd-btn">
	    <div class="span8">
			<input class="btn" type="button" value="发表博客">
			<input class="btn" type="button" value="存为草稿">
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
</form>

